commit message:
Fix chart rendering (issue #1)

The battery level was not accurate: an offset was added.

The chart is now rendered in a Bitmap without a WeakReference, so that
this cache can be properly recycled when the view is destroyed.
Use ProGuard to remove unused bytecode (issue #3)
Use lighter colors for battery chart (issue #2)
Add a preference for selecting a time interval (issue #4)
Delete oldest events when the phone starts (issue #5)
Do not run export if the external storage is not available (issue #7)
